title = "Donate to Angband"
<h2>Donate</h2>

<p>If you want to donate to the server hosting costs for rephial.org, then you can do so using PayPal below.  When you donate, if you wish to remain anonymous, please say so.  Accounts will be published here with who donated and when.  Angband uses up the lion's share of the resources on the server, but we do use it for some other sites and email too.  If you do donate, thanks very much!

<p>Note that when donating, enter your amount and then click "Update Total" before doing anything else, or PayPal tends to forget the amount you enter.

